{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d17-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9173"},"text":"§ 9173.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Museum services activities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d18-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Director, subject to the policy advice of the Museum and Library Services Board, may enter into arrangements, including grants, contracts, cooperative agreements, and other forms of assistance, with museums, States, local governments, and other entities as the Director considers appropriate, to pay the Federal share of the cost of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d19-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting museums in providing learning and access to collections, information, and educational resources in a variety of formats (including exhibitions, programs, publications, and websites) for individuals of all ages;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting museums in building learning partnerships with the Nation’s schools, including tribal schools, and developing museum resources, capabilities, and programs in support of State and local efforts to offer a well-rounded educational experience to all students;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" supporting the conservation and preservation of museum collections, including efforts to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provide optimal conditions for storage, exhibition, and use;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" prepare for and respond to disasters and emergency situations;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" establish endowments for conservation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d1f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" curate, stabilize, and organize object-related information; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d20-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/3/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" train museum staff in collections care;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d21-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting efforts at the State level to leverage museum resources, including statewide assessments of museum services and needs and development of State plans to improve and maximize museum services through the State;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d22-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" creating shared technology tools and data resources, and developing museum staff training plans to improve and maximize museum services through organizations such as museum associations, professional networks, community-based organizations, and foundations, and through other collaborative mechanisms;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d23-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" stimulating greater collaboration, in order to share resources and strengthen communities, among museums and—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d24-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" libraries;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d25-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" schools;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d26-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" institutions of higher education;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d27-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" international, Federal, State, regional, tribal, and local agencies or organizations;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d28-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" nongovernmental organizations;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d29-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/F"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"F"},"text":"(F)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" other community organizations; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/6/G"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"G"},"text":"(G)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" other relevant research and policy organizations;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" encouraging the use of new and emerging technologies and media, including new ways to disseminate information, engage varied audiences in experiential learning, and support teachers and students to enhance access to and engagement with museum collections, programs, and services;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting museums in developing, carrying out, and providing programs and services that meet the needs of communities throughout the Nation, including people of diverse geographic, cultural, and socioeconomic backgrounds, individuals with disabilities, residents of rural and urban areas, Native Americans, military families, veterans, and caregivers, and for State institutions;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9"},"text":"(9)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting professional development and technical assistance programs to enhance museum operations, and the skills of museum staff, at all levels, and to support the development of the next generation of museum leaders and professionals, in order to ensure the highest standards in all aspects of museum operations;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/10"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10"},"text":"(10)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" supporting museums in research, program evaluation, and the collection and dissemination of information to museum professionals and the public;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d2f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/11"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11"},"text":"(11)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" encouraging, supporting, and disseminating model programs of museum and library collaboration;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d30-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/12"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12"},"text":"(12)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" enabling museums to serve as anchor institutions to support community revitalization and the creation of opportunities for advancement; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d31-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/a/13"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"13"},"text":"(13)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" developing public and private partnerships with other agencies and community-based organizations to expand and enhance museum services.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d32-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Federal share","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d33-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" 50 percent","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in paragraph (2), the Federal share described in subsection (a) shall be not more than 50 percent.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d34-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Greater than 50 percent","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Director may use not more than 20 percent of the funds made available under this subchapter for a fiscal year to enter into arrangements under subsection (a) for which the Federal share may be greater than 50 percent.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d35-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Operational expenses","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No funds for operational expenses may be provided under this section to any entity that is not a museum.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d36-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Review and evaluation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d37-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Director shall establish procedures for reviewing and evaluating arrangements described in subsection (a) entered into under this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d38-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Grant distribution","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In awarding grants, the Director shall take into consideration the equitable distribution of grants to museums of various types and sizes and to different geographic areas of the United States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d39-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Applications for technical assistance","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d3a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Director may use not more than 10 percent of the funds appropriated to carry out this subchapter for technical assistance.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d3b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/c/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Individual museums","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Individual museums may receive not more than 3 technical assistance awards under subparagraph (A). Subsequent awards for technical assistance shall be subject to review outside the Institute.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d3c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9173/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Services for Native Americans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"From amounts appropriated under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s9176"},"text":"section 9176 of this title","children":[],"tail":", the Director shall reserve 2.25 percent to award grants to, or enter into contracts or cooperative agreements with, Indian tribes and organizations that primarily serve and represent Native Hawaiians (as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7517"},"text":"section 7517 of this title","children":[],"tail":"), to enable such tribes and organizations to carry out the activities described in subsection (a)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0e5d9d3d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/462/tII/s274"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–462, title II, § 274","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 273, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/dA/tI/s101/e/tVII/s702"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–208, div. A, title I, § 101(e) [title VII, § 702]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3009-233"},"text":"110 Stat. 3009–233","children":[],"tail":", 3009–303; renumbered § 274 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/81/tIII"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–81, title III","children":[],"tail":", §§ 303, 306(1), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-09-25"},"text":"Sept. 25, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/1000"},"text":"117 Stat. 1000","children":[],"tail":", 1002; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/tIII/s303"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, title III, § 303","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/3603"},"text":"124 Stat. 3603","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/tIX/s9215/aaa/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, title IX, § 9215(aaa)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/2184"},"text":"129 Stat. 2184","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/5420"},"text":"132 Stat. 5420","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0e5d9d3e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0e5d9d3f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0e5d9d40-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/462/s274"},"text":"section 274 of Pub. L. 94–462","children":[],"tail":" was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s9174"},"text":"section 9174 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/81"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–81","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id0e5d9d41-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (2) and struck out former par. (2) which read as follows: “supporting museums in building learning partnerships with the Nation’s schools and developing museum resources and programs in support of State and local school curricula;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3)(D), (E). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subpar. (D) and redesignated former subpar. (D) as (E)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(5)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (5). Former par. (5) redesignated (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(4)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (5) as (6). Former par. (6) redesignated (7)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/6/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(6)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added subpar. (C). Former subpar. (C) redesignated (D)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6)(D). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/6/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(6)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (C), redesignated subpar. (C) as (D) and inserted “tribal,” after “regional,”. Former subpar. (D) redesignated (E)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6)(E), (F). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/6/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(6)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (D), redesignated subpars. (D) and (E) as (E) and (F), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6)(G). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/6/D"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(6)(D)","children":[],"tail":"–(F), added subpar. (G)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(7). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(4)","children":[],"tail":", (7), redesignated par. (4) as (7), struck it out, and added a new par. (7). Prior to amendment, par. read as follows: “supporting efforts at the State level to leverage museum resources, including statewide assessments of museum services and needs and development of State plans to improve and maximize museum services through the State;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", struck out par. (7) which read as follows: “supporting museums in providing services to people of diverse geographic, cultural, and socioeconomic backgrounds and to individuals with disabilities;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(8). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(8)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (8) and struck out former par. (8) which read as follows: “supporting museums in developing and carrying out specialized programs for specific segments of the public, such as programs for urban neighborhoods, rural areas, Indian reservations, and State institutions;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(12), (13). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/a/9"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(a)(9)","children":[],"tail":"–(11), added pars. (12) and (13)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/c/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(c)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", inserted period at end."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(3)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/c/1/B/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(c)(1)(B)(i)","children":[],"tail":", amended subpar. (A) of par. (3) to duplicate amendment made by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/2/C/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(2)(C)(i)","children":[],"tail":", which had been directed to subpar. (A) of par. (2) but executed to par. (3) to reflect the probable intent of Congress, thus resulting in no change in text. See 2010 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(3)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/c/1/B/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(c)(1)(B)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", amended subpar. (B) of par. (3) to duplicate amendment made by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/2/C/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(2)(C)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", which had been directed to subpar. (B) of par. (2) but executed to par. (3) to reflect the probable intent of Congress, thus resulting in no change in text. See 2010 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/410/s18/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–410, § 18(b)","children":[],"tail":", (c)(2), substituted “2.25 percent” for “1.75 percent” and made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s9176"},"text":"section 9176 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95","children":[],"tail":" made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7517"},"text":"section 7517 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “, States, local governments,” after “with museums” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3) to (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", (C), added pars. (3) to (5), redesignated former par. (5) as (6), and struck out former pars. (3) and (4) which read as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) supporting museums in assessing, conserving, researching, maintaining, and exhibiting their collections, and in providing educational programs to the public through the use of their collections;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(4) stimulating greater collaboration among museums, libraries, schools, and other community organizations in order to share resources and strengthen communities;”.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", (D), redesignated par. (5) as (6) and substituted “media, including new ways to disseminate information,” for “broadcast media”. Former par. (6) redesignated (7)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(7), (8). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated pars. (6) and (7) as (7) and (8), respectively. Former par. (8) redesignated (9)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(9). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", (E), redesignated par. (8) as (9) and substituted “, and the skills of museum staff, at all levels, and to support the development of the next generation of museum leaders and professionals,” for “at all levels,”. Former par. (9) redesignated (10)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(10), (11). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated pars. (9) and (10) as (10) and (11), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(2), (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (B), added par. (2) and redesignated former par. (2) as (3)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(3)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/2/C/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(2)(C)(i)","children":[],"tail":", which directed that “awards” be struck out after “assistance” in subpar. (A) of par. (2), was executed by making the amendment in subpar. (A) of par. (3) to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the intervening redesignation of par. (2) as (3). See above."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(3)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/340/s303/2/C/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–340, § 303(2)(C)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", which directed the substitution of “. Subsequent” for “, but subsequent” in subpar. (B) of par. (2), was executed by making the amendment in subpar. (B) of par. (3) to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the intervening redesignation of par. (2) as (3). See above."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2003—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/81/s303"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–81, § 303","children":[],"tail":", amended section catchline and text generally. Prior to amendment, section contained provisions which in subsec. (a) authorized the Director to make grants to museums to pay for the Federal share of the cost of increasing and improving museum services, in subsec. (b) authorized the Director to enter into contracts and cooperative agreements with appropriate entities to pay for the Federal share of enabling the entities to undertake projects designed to strengthen museum services, in subsec. (c) established the Federal share, and in subsec. (d) required the Director to establish procedures for reviewing and evaluating grants, contracts, and cooperative agreements entered into under this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id0e5d9d42-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id0e5d9d43-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2015 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", except with respect to certain noncompetitive programs and competitive programs, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s5"},"text":"section 5 of Pub. L. 114–95","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s6301"},"text":"section 6301 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
